text: La Vôge-les-Bains is a commune in the department of Vosges, eastern France. The municipality was established on 1 January 2017 by merger of the former communes of Bains-les-Bains (the seat), Harsault and Hautmougey.Arrêté préfectoral 5 December 2016 == See also == *Communes of the Vosges department == References == Category:Communes of Vosges (department)
title: La Vôge-les-Bains
